package DESCRIPTION file

Source: R/description.R
pac_description.Rd

package DESCRIPTION file taken locally or if remotely then from GITHUB CRAN mirror or CRAN website.

pac_description(pac, version = NULL, at = NULL, local = FALSE, lib.loc = NULL)

Arguments

pac

character a package name.
version

character package version. Default: NULL
at

Date. Default: NULL
local

logical if to use local library. Default: FALSE
lib.loc

character used optionally when local is equal TRUE. Default: NULL

Value

list with names proper for DESCRIPTION file fields.

Examples

pac_description("dplyr", version = "0.8.0")
